WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.090
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.090 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 16]

01:39.870 --> 01:40.460
Lei!

01:43.350 --> 01:44.020
Lei!

01:52.230 --> 01:53.540
Lifei, you've worked so hard.

01:54.510 --> 01:56.410
Only you from Zhuiyu Peak have made it to the top eight.

01:56.840 --> 01:57.490
I owe it

01:57.510 --> 01:59.460
to you all for cheering me on

02:00.590 --> 02:02.690
and our master for training me well.

02:03.950 --> 02:05.050
Good.

02:06.790 --> 02:08.570
All eight competitors tomorrow are formidable.

02:08.790 --> 02:10.130
Your opponent, Tang De,

02:10.150 --> 02:11.660
is the best of Wengu Peak.

02:12.150 --> 02:14.570
Your little tricks won't work much.

02:14.960 --> 02:15.780
True.

02:16.470 --> 02:17.890
You will lose tomorrow.

02:18.560 --> 02:19.410
No point in massaging you.

02:21.960 --> 02:22.540
He really stops.

02:25.030 --> 02:28.940
Master, teach me some clever moves!

02:30.120 --> 02:31.890
Last-minute tips won't do much.

02:31.960 --> 02:33.410
It's good to make it to the top eight.

02:37.910 --> 02:38.450
Go to sleep.

02:39.710 --> 02:40.260
But...

02:43.710 --> 02:46.010
Bedtime now.

02:46.590 --> 02:47.450
Go to bed.

02:48.280 --> 02:49.850
Better try than not.

03:00.150 --> 03:01.100
Nice place!

03:02.430 --> 03:03.410
I'll cram last-minute tips right here.

03:11.080 --> 03:11.610
Who's there?

03:38.560 --> 03:39.340
Are you okay?

03:41.280 --> 03:42.010
I'm fine.

03:43.120 --> 03:43.660
Go.

03:46.280 --> 03:47.890
Did you get hurt picking fruit?

03:49.400 --> 03:50.100
Let me check.

03:55.760 --> 03:59.240
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

04:00.000 --> 04:02.240
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

04:02.680 --> 04:05.720
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

04:06.360 --> 04:08.640
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

04:09.440 --> 04:12.920
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

04:13.280 --> 04:15.560
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

04:15.800 --> 04:16.890
What are you doing?

04:16.890 --> 04:18.470
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

04:18.470 --> 04:18.850
You...

04:19.760 --> 04:21.480
♪Reign supreme♪

04:21.480 --> 04:22.980
What are you doing?

04:24.160 --> 04:24.730
Let go.

04:24.730 --> 04:27.120
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

04:27.120 --> 04:27.730
Let go.

04:32.270 --> 04:32.780
Lifei!

04:34.120 --> 04:34.660
Lifei.

04:36.270 --> 04:37.020
Don't leave me.

04:39.040 --> 04:39.660
I like you.

05:00.160 --> 05:01.290
I should've ignored you.

05:12.560 --> 05:14.290
If they find my demonic corruption,

05:15.070 --> 05:16.220
I'll be kicked out of Wuyue Court.

05:18.270 --> 05:19.140
I mustn't leave her.

05:30.510 --> 05:32.100
After searching all sixteen peaks last night,

05:32.920 --> 05:35.580
we found up to 11 disciples secretly

05:35.920 --> 05:37.370
practicing demonic arts.

05:37.680 --> 05:41.020
They've been expelled with their cultivation crippled.

05:42.160 --> 05:44.660
The demon clan tries to split us with evil arts.

05:45.120 --> 05:47.250
This is critical to our court.

05:47.800 --> 05:49.660
Any disciple with a wavering Dao heart

05:49.680 --> 05:51.810
who secretly practices demonic arts for quick power

05:52.240 --> 05:54.610
shall be treated as demons and slain without mercy.

05:57.720 --> 06:00.490
He was pretending to be miserable. Hateful!

06:01.560 --> 06:03.100
Tang De practiced demonic arts,

06:03.510 --> 06:04.850
so he is disqualified.

06:05.430 --> 06:07.700
Jiang Lifei advances straight to the semi-finals.

06:08.160 --> 06:10.780
The rest of the top-eight duels go on.

06:13.120 --> 06:14.340
Lifei, amazing!

06:14.360 --> 06:14.730
I...

06:19.510 --> 06:20.900
This is ridiculous.

06:21.190 --> 06:23.250
Isn't the tournament all about real strength?

06:23.510 --> 06:24.700
Cuixuan, this...

06:24.830 --> 06:26.340
Don't talk nonsense.

06:26.560 --> 06:28.850
Baifu, it's just luck.

06:29.120 --> 06:31.660
Accept it and be jealous.

06:33.750 --> 06:34.700
Thank you.

06:41.720 --> 06:43.370
My luck won't last long.

06:44.190 --> 06:46.340
Yue has seniority and strong cultivation,

06:47.070 --> 06:48.140
plus she's not scared of bugs.

06:50.920 --> 06:52.370
I can only try every last trick.

06:57.190 --> 06:58.050
Qin?

07:00.040 --> 07:01.140
Are you also practicing at Yuelian Pond?

07:02.920 --> 07:04.100
I knew you'd come,

07:04.560 --> 07:05.460
so I waited here for you.

07:07.430 --> 07:08.540
You want to win the tournament, right?

07:09.000 --> 07:10.050
Since you're in the semi-finals,

07:10.510 --> 07:12.100
give it your all tomorrow.

07:14.040 --> 07:15.930
Are you going to teach me advanced spirit arts?

07:22.830 --> 07:24.170
Hold your breath, and close your eyes.

07:25.750 --> 07:26.370
Close your eyes.

07:34.750 --> 07:35.610
Try to accept me

07:36.390 --> 07:37.340
and merge our spirit energy.

07:41.120 --> 07:41.850
This isn't proper.

07:43.510 --> 07:44.610
Don't you want to win?

07:45.160 --> 07:46.100
Merging our spirit energy

07:46.360 --> 07:47.980
is the fastest way to boost your power.

07:49.190 --> 07:51.170
But only cultivation partners do this.

07:51.630 --> 07:52.850
I read about it in storybooks.

07:53.190 --> 07:53.980
Merging spirit energy means

07:54.000 --> 07:55.660
giving your whole heart and soul.

07:56.000 --> 07:56.930
Only for your beloved.

07:57.720 --> 07:58.370
Lifei,

07:59.830 --> 08:00.850
actually,

08:03.160 --> 08:04.020
I have

08:04.430 --> 08:06.250
liked you all along.

08:08.480 --> 08:09.490
Will you be my cultivation partner?

08:09.950 --> 08:10.930
Wait.

08:11.510 --> 08:12.730
I don't feel that way about you.

08:14.040 --> 08:17.610
Is there something wrong with me?

08:17.950 --> 08:20.290
No. You're perfect in every way.

08:21.560 --> 08:23.930
It's me who's unworthy.

08:24.310 --> 08:26.410
With weak spirit power, I just joined the sect,

08:26.750 --> 08:28.980
and I'm not romantic at all, so I'm not the one for you.

08:30.270 --> 08:31.290
You're overthinking.

08:31.870 --> 08:32.930
I believe we're a perfect match.

08:33.040 --> 08:35.050
I don't think so.

08:38.510 --> 08:40.420
I'm returning this flying ribbon.

08:40.670 --> 08:41.580
Give it to a stronger,

08:41.600 --> 08:42.730
prettier senior sister instead.

08:43.030 --> 08:46.010
Lifei, I truly like you.

08:47.080 --> 08:48.460
Will you give me a chance?

08:49.480 --> 08:51.420
Let me help you win the tournament first,

08:51.750 --> 08:52.250
alright?

08:53.600 --> 08:55.980
No need. I want to win,

08:56.790 --> 08:57.850
but I'll never act against my heart.

08:59.200 --> 08:59.850
See you.

09:04.320 --> 09:04.820
Wait.

09:20.360 --> 09:20.770
Who's there?

09:27.080 --> 09:27.890
Lei Xiuyuan.

09:29.790 --> 09:32.850
Qin, what's wrong now?

09:34.080 --> 09:35.700
I wanted to chat with her a little longer.

09:36.080 --> 09:37.130
Stay out of this.

09:37.600 --> 09:38.340
Qin,

09:41.000 --> 09:42.100
I've said all I need to.

09:42.480 --> 09:43.580
There's nothing more.

09:46.270 --> 09:47.060
Let me send you back.

09:49.150 --> 09:49.650
No need.

10:12.510 --> 10:14.180
What rotten luck!

10:15.080 --> 10:16.460
My last-minute plan failed again.

10:23.030 --> 10:24.370
Lei Xiuyuan, come out!

10:36.480 --> 10:38.730
You are too weak to protect yourself,

10:39.120 --> 10:40.250
yet you trust others blindly.

10:41.000 --> 10:42.490
My worst mistake was trusting you above all else.

10:42.910 --> 10:43.580
You'd better

10:44.150 --> 10:44.890
forfeit tomorrow's duel.

10:46.790 --> 10:47.250
Again.

10:48.080 --> 10:48.820
You've lost.

10:52.960 --> 10:54.300
I haven't fallen, so I haven't lost.

10:54.870 --> 10:55.300
Again.

10:57.120 --> 10:58.010
The fight isn't over yet.

11:05.510 --> 11:07.700
Chiyan Stone of Xingzheng Hall.

11:08.840 --> 11:09.490
Lifei,

11:10.150 --> 11:12.100
I heard Wuyue Court is holding a tournament.

11:13.200 --> 11:15.100
This stone can summon a fire wall

11:15.440 --> 11:17.580
to block a fatal blow. It may help you.

11:21.000 --> 11:21.850
Thank you, Tongzhou.

11:26.910 --> 11:27.810
Senior Sister, you'll win.

11:27.830 --> 11:29.140
Yeah, we believe in you!

11:32.430 --> 11:33.090
Place your bets!

11:33.110 --> 11:34.380
Lifei, listen to me.

11:34.560 --> 11:35.780
First, the Monkey Steals Peach trick.

11:37.160 --> 11:38.860
Does anyone want to place a bet?

11:38.960 --> 11:39.650
It'll work.

11:40.150 --> 11:41.090
Do what I said.

11:41.110 --> 11:42.220
That's such a dirty move!

11:43.630 --> 11:44.180
Lifei.

11:44.590 --> 11:45.660
Just do as we said.

11:45.660 --> 11:46.500
Lifei.

11:48.630 --> 11:49.250
You know what?

11:49.660 --> 11:51.250
I cast my fortune today.

11:51.520 --> 11:54.020
It said I'd have great windfall luck.

11:54.270 --> 11:55.700
Then I thought and realized

11:56.360 --> 11:59.450
you're the biggest underdog here.

12:00.430 --> 12:01.340
As the saying goes,

12:01.510 --> 12:04.060
the ignorant fears nothing; the shameless prevails.

12:04.360 --> 12:05.340
So

12:07.150 --> 12:08.300
I set up

12:08.510 --> 12:09.900
this betting pool

12:10.320 --> 12:12.530
for your duel against Yue.

12:14.040 --> 12:15.620
Anyone want to join?

12:15.660 --> 12:16.340
What are the odds?

12:16.870 --> 12:18.900
One to one if you bet on Yue.

12:19.080 --> 12:21.300
One to fifty if you bet on Lifei to win.

12:21.830 --> 12:22.410
Come on.

12:22.430 --> 12:24.450
Hey, you there, want to join?

12:25.320 --> 12:26.020
Come on.

12:26.150 --> 12:27.260
Count me in!

12:27.280 --> 12:28.850
- I'll bet on Yue. - Me too!

12:29.230 --> 12:30.100
Let me have a look.

12:30.790 --> 12:32.060
Alright, put them here.

12:33.310 --> 12:34.060
Who're you betting on?

12:34.640 --> 12:35.570
- Okay. - Wait.

12:36.720 --> 12:37.900
Hardly anyone bet on me winning.

12:39.390 --> 12:40.540
Don't look down on it.

12:41.000 --> 12:42.370
I bet everything on you.

12:42.760 --> 12:43.540
Fight well, Lifei.

12:43.950 --> 12:45.620
You're my ticket to wealth!

12:46.480 --> 12:47.740
All bets placed.

12:48.200 --> 12:48.900
Let's watch the duel.

12:49.150 --> 12:50.130
- Okay. - Go for it!

12:50.590 --> 12:52.770
- I'm rooting for you, Lifei. - Go for it!

13:01.390 --> 13:02.180
Yue.

13:06.080 --> 13:06.980
Lifei,

13:08.030 --> 13:09.700
I won't hold back.

13:13.390 --> 13:13.900
Begin.

13:56.880 --> 13:58.250
The identical moves.

14:17.670 --> 14:18.530
Her zither strings snapped.

14:18.950 --> 14:21.020
- What to do? - What's going on?

14:24.040 --> 14:25.460
He even taught you the metal technique?

15:38.950 --> 15:39.580
I'm lost.

15:46.240 --> 15:47.490
Incredible!

15:49.510 --> 15:50.540
Great!

15:52.560 --> 15:53.690
Well done, Lifei!

15:54.640 --> 15:57.450
- Impressive. - Unbelievable win!

16:46.150 --> 16:48.770
Let go! Let go of her!

16:49.960 --> 16:52.370
Boy, focus on your duel.

16:52.390 --> 16:53.100
You're holding on so tight.

16:53.120 --> 16:54.250
Let's go.

17:26.830 --> 17:29.380
Lei, I won't hold back.

17:55.680 --> 17:59.490
Lei Xiuyuan is fearless like a new calf.

18:00.000 --> 18:01.900
He fought Qin to a draw.

18:02.070 --> 18:03.940
Promising youth.

18:23.480 --> 18:25.980
Cuixuan, you care so deeply for Qin

18:26.350 --> 18:29.050
that you even passed down the Yin-Yang Tribulation Mirror to him.

19:01.680 --> 19:02.460
Lei,

19:03.790 --> 19:04.810
you're too green.

19:07.510 --> 19:10.050
Surrender now, and I'll stop.

19:31.550 --> 19:32.380
Just surrender.

19:35.480 --> 19:37.900
Take my advice:

19:38.240 --> 19:39.180
The higher you hold your head,

19:39.640 --> 19:41.420
the harder you'll fall.

19:46.640 --> 19:47.860
You're not worthy to beat me.

19:48.960 --> 19:51.700
Stay away from Jiang Lifei from now on.

19:53.960 --> 19:55.050
That Longyuan Sword

19:55.400 --> 19:57.940
was left for you by the former sect leader.

19:58.920 --> 19:59.570
Guangwei,

20:00.500 --> 20:03.140
you truly look out for Lei.

20:23.310 --> 20:27.090
Great!

20:27.110 --> 20:30.620
Dragon Roars Across the Sky, the sixth-level art.

20:31.460 --> 20:32.090
Guangwei,

20:32.350 --> 20:34.770
you've hidden him too well.

20:36.590 --> 20:38.570
This is the real combat.

21:08.750 --> 21:11.730
Lei Xiuyuan of Yaoguang Peak wins.

21:20.660 --> 21:21.730
Jiang Lifei

21:22.510 --> 21:25.010
versus Lei Xiuyuan in two hours.

21:37.270 --> 21:40.180
I'm too gravely injured to fight the final.

21:42.420 --> 21:43.570
I will forfeit.

21:45.740 --> 21:46.050
What?

21:47.460 --> 21:49.010
- Why? - How can he just give up?

21:49.030 --> 21:49.620
Yeah.

21:49.940 --> 21:51.460
- What's going on? - He fears?

21:51.790 --> 21:52.940
I can't understand.

21:53.590 --> 21:54.620
Is he forfeiting?

21:55.030 --> 21:56.490
Does that mean...?

22:01.440 --> 22:02.940
- Is that allowed? - I want to ask the same.

22:03.900 --> 22:04.570
Why?

22:05.830 --> 22:06.490
Yue, please help me.

22:12.110 --> 22:12.730
Let's go.

22:32.310 --> 22:34.090
You won!

22:34.220 --> 22:36.620
- Lifei, you won. - We won!

22:37.020 --> 22:39.220
Thanks to you, we're rich now!

22:39.510 --> 22:40.220
We won.

22:45.900 --> 22:47.620
- We won! - Great!

23:01.110 --> 23:01.770
Be careful.

23:06.660 --> 23:07.010
Sit down.

23:14.020 --> 23:15.050
Let me treat your wounds first.

23:25.460 --> 23:26.730
You lied. You still have strength left.

23:28.350 --> 23:29.180
You let Jiang

23:29.220 --> 23:30.570
take first place on purpose.

23:31.420 --> 23:33.090
Thankfully, this was only a duel.

23:33.700 --> 23:34.860
If it were a life-or-death battle,

23:34.900 --> 23:36.660
you'd have sacrificed yourself for her!

23:37.310 --> 23:39.940
Yeah. It's just a duel anyway.

23:41.500 --> 23:43.220
Why did you intend to kill her?

23:44.030 --> 23:44.570
I...

23:48.030 --> 23:49.620
If I wanted her dead,

23:50.420 --> 23:51.810
do you think a mere Chiyan Stone

23:51.830 --> 23:52.900
could stop me?

23:56.460 --> 23:56.980
Truth is,

24:00.220 --> 24:02.730
I could kill her anytime.

24:07.830 --> 24:08.660
I dare you!

24:16.110 --> 24:19.290
I told you your talent is unmatched.

24:19.940 --> 24:21.420
You could become an immortal

24:21.590 --> 24:22.730
or a sect leader,

24:23.220 --> 24:24.660
bound for greatness.

24:25.220 --> 24:26.770
Our master holds high hopes...

24:26.790 --> 24:27.980
My plans are none of your business.

24:31.220 --> 24:34.290
You've crossed the line time and again.

24:35.750 --> 24:37.570
What do you want from me?

24:41.740 --> 24:42.980
What do I want?

24:47.180 --> 24:48.290
Have you forgotten?

24:51.030 --> 24:53.010
I'd lay down my life for you.

24:54.260 --> 24:58.090
My clan's fate rests with My Lord.

24:58.550 --> 25:01.490
I'd die without regret.

25:07.830 --> 25:08.490
Whoever you truly are,

25:09.880 --> 25:11.140
I joined Wuyue Court for only one person.

25:12.070 --> 25:13.010
Nothing else matters.

25:14.510 --> 25:17.530
Please stay away from me from now on.

25:37.720 --> 25:38.380
Master.

25:46.030 --> 25:49.010
Well, well.

25:50.240 --> 25:52.620
You pleaded severe injuries to withdraw,

25:54.640 --> 25:56.700
so I shall indulge your request.

25:59.640 --> 26:00.290
Master.

26:02.750 --> 26:05.770
You reckless boy! I told you repeatedly

26:06.000 --> 26:06.860
to stand out

26:06.880 --> 26:08.860
among Wuyue Court's young disciples.

26:09.240 --> 26:10.730
Yet you acted foolishly

26:10.960 --> 26:12.860
and recklessly, all for a girl.

26:18.720 --> 26:20.380
Since you remain stubborn,

26:20.640 --> 26:22.730
I'll cripple your spirit root

26:23.350 --> 26:26.220
to stop you from going astray and endangering the sect.

26:37.270 --> 26:39.460
Master, he's young and impulsive.

26:39.510 --> 26:41.050
He merely lost his sense for a while.

26:41.590 --> 26:42.810
Please spare him.

26:43.350 --> 26:44.940
I'll guide him well.

26:50.960 --> 26:51.570
Master.

26:54.640 --> 26:56.770
I'll grant you one last chance.

26:57.590 --> 26:59.940
I'll show no mercy if you stay obsessed.

27:08.400 --> 27:08.900
Stand up.

27:14.590 --> 27:17.220
Is Jiang Lifei worth all this?

27:22.750 --> 27:23.700
Wake up.

27:24.110 --> 27:26.010
She's your destined tribulation.

27:28.720 --> 27:29.530
Conduct yourself wisely.

27:45.920 --> 27:47.660
Enter the Achillea Bead.

28:29.680 --> 28:30.940
I wonder where my master is

28:31.510 --> 28:32.490
and if he's safe.

29:24.790 --> 29:25.420
Wait.

29:25.920 --> 29:26.530
Cuixuan.

29:28.960 --> 29:30.940
What are you doing?

29:30.960 --> 29:33.810
The Achillea Bead is a rare treasure.

29:34.400 --> 29:37.380
It dissolved instantly, pouring all its spirit energy into her.

29:37.510 --> 29:38.660
That's strange.

29:39.790 --> 29:41.860
Jiang Lifei must be suspicious.

29:42.830 --> 29:44.660
What's suspicious about it?

29:44.750 --> 29:46.290
She shares fate with it,

29:46.310 --> 29:47.570
and it chose to gift her energy freely.

29:47.590 --> 29:48.730
What's the problem?

29:50.160 --> 29:51.050
No such occurrence

29:51.070 --> 29:53.010
has happened in centuries.

29:53.160 --> 29:56.010
Luck alone can't explain this.

30:01.070 --> 30:01.700
Cuixuan,

30:03.110 --> 30:04.180
I brought her

30:04.240 --> 30:06.660
to Wuyue Court long ago.

30:06.960 --> 30:08.860
She bears a unique, spirit-attracting physique

30:09.590 --> 30:11.180
that caused

30:11.510 --> 30:13.290
the Achillea's strange reaction.

30:15.720 --> 30:16.620
Spirit-attracting?

30:21.440 --> 30:24.420
I've been weak since childhood,

30:25.510 --> 30:28.220
and the spirits always come to me.

30:28.240 --> 30:29.490
It's not my fault.

30:33.960 --> 30:35.290
Blame me for this.

30:35.510 --> 30:37.050
I'll fetch a protective talisman

30:37.070 --> 30:37.810
for you right now.

30:38.030 --> 30:38.420
Let's go.

30:38.830 --> 30:40.420
The Achillea's chaotic power

30:41.160 --> 30:44.090
floods Lifei all at once.

30:44.310 --> 30:45.900
I'm afraid her meridians can't bear it.

30:46.830 --> 30:49.660
I'll take you back to Cuihua Peak

30:49.790 --> 30:52.010
to stabilize your cultivation.

30:52.200 --> 30:53.570
Don't bother

30:53.790 --> 30:55.140
with this trivial thing.

30:55.480 --> 30:56.530
I can handle this myself.

30:57.440 --> 30:59.250
The tournament is over,

30:59.270 --> 31:00.330
so we'll take our leave.

31:01.270 --> 31:03.700
Farewell, everyone!

31:04.070 --> 31:05.330
Zhuiyu Peak, go!

31:06.640 --> 31:07.290
Go.

31:07.680 --> 31:09.980
Disciples of Zhuiyu Peak, let's go.

31:10.510 --> 31:11.010
Go.

31:11.350 --> 31:12.220
Go.

31:29.350 --> 31:30.090
Focus your mind,

31:32.240 --> 31:33.180
channel energy,

31:35.590 --> 31:36.180
and strike once.

31:39.160 --> 31:39.530
This...

31:50.400 --> 31:51.980
Just as I thought.

31:52.550 --> 31:54.330
The thousand-year-old Achillea's

31:54.640 --> 31:56.330
spirit energy in your body

31:56.590 --> 31:59.180
has boosted your power

31:59.200 --> 32:01.010
to at least the fourth level.

32:01.790 --> 32:03.330
Am I strong now?

32:03.960 --> 32:04.530
Come here.

32:08.030 --> 32:09.490
Don't get carried away.

32:10.200 --> 32:12.570
You think more spirit power is something to rejoice in?

32:13.270 --> 32:16.460
Unregulated surging power will devour you.

32:16.790 --> 32:19.460
Now you need to practice hard

32:19.680 --> 32:21.090
to master and integrate it

32:21.110 --> 32:23.140
before you wield it freely.

32:23.830 --> 32:25.290
Now, understand?

32:25.960 --> 32:27.330
Thought I'd gotten free luck.

32:28.400 --> 32:29.770
This power is too risky to wield.

32:32.350 --> 32:34.620
Lifei, what did you see

32:34.640 --> 32:35.660
in the illusion?

32:37.310 --> 32:38.220
Nothing yet

32:38.880 --> 32:40.220
before Elder Cuixuan attacked.

32:40.550 --> 32:41.730
So petty

32:41.960 --> 32:43.050
over a little spirit energy.

32:45.680 --> 32:47.180
Don't be ungrateful.

32:47.590 --> 32:48.770
A little?

32:49.030 --> 32:50.010
You drained

32:50.030 --> 32:51.660
the spirit plant completely.

32:51.790 --> 32:53.490
I felt embarrassed for you.

32:54.110 --> 32:55.900
I didn't mean to.

32:57.240 --> 32:59.290
Stay

32:59.400 --> 33:00.490
on the peak lately.

33:00.550 --> 33:01.660
Don't wander off.

33:05.480 --> 33:08.860
And never cross Elder Cuixuan.

33:12.240 --> 33:14.140
Master, head back and wait for dinner.

33:16.000 --> 33:16.810
Are you cooking?

33:16.880 --> 33:17.700
Of course.

33:21.160 --> 33:21.730
Off you go.

33:57.000 --> 33:57.810
Master!

34:09.440 --> 34:09.980
Ma...

34:26.320 --> 34:27.570
Better check it out,

34:28.510 --> 34:29.900
or I'll keep worrying.

34:49.960 --> 34:50.860
There's a restriction spell.

36:16.190 --> 36:16.900
Come with me.

36:57.280 --> 36:58.210
Don't act on your own again.

37:33.920 --> 37:35.820
Demonic energy leakage in Lilie Valley.

37:53.280 --> 37:56.380
How crafty! Thanks to the demonic energy,

37:57.190 --> 37:58.490
or we'd be caught.

38:02.630 --> 38:03.380
I haven't asked.

38:05.110 --> 38:05.860
What are you doing here?

38:06.480 --> 38:07.090
Stalking me?

38:08.800 --> 38:10.380
You just absorbed energy from the Achillea Bead.

38:11.110 --> 38:12.260
I worried you'd feel unwell.

38:17.360 --> 38:18.380
Cuixuan is so upset.

38:19.150 --> 38:20.780
There must be a secret hidden on Hushe Peak.

38:21.360 --> 38:22.050
Head back to your peak.

38:22.510 --> 38:23.130
Keep quiet.

38:23.630 --> 38:24.530
Don't alert them.

38:25.280 --> 38:26.420
Stay out of my business,

38:27.000 --> 38:27.610
understand?

38:41.760 --> 38:42.570
For the Vermilion Fruit,

38:44.000 --> 38:44.900
the tournament,

38:45.960 --> 38:46.820
and what happened today,

38:51.190 --> 38:51.860
thank you.

38:54.400 --> 38:55.380
I'll remember all of this

38:55.440 --> 38:56.210
and repay you someday.

39:12.590 --> 39:14.650
Lilie Valley is our sect's forbidden area.

39:15.280 --> 39:16.780
Sealed jointly by past elders,

39:16.960 --> 39:17.860
it's impenetrable.

39:18.840 --> 39:21.130
It's stayed safe for centuries.

39:21.840 --> 39:23.300
Why is there demonic energy leakage?

39:23.710 --> 39:26.940
Perhaps the demons trapped inside linger,

39:27.670 --> 39:29.050
struggling in their last gasp.

39:30.960 --> 39:32.690
The valley lacks spirit energy,

39:32.760 --> 39:34.210
and they've been bound for five centuries.

39:34.590 --> 39:35.460
Even alive,

39:35.920 --> 39:37.380
they're crippled

39:38.710 --> 39:40.010
and cannot break free.

39:40.880 --> 39:43.570
Their souls endure centuries of captivity,

39:44.710 --> 39:46.740
which means the demonic spirits are far too powerful.

39:47.510 --> 39:48.530
We must stay vigilant.

39:53.230 --> 39:54.530
This leakage proves

39:54.960 --> 39:56.090
the seal

39:56.920 --> 39:59.090
in the valley is damaged.

39:59.760 --> 40:02.690
First, we must locate and repair

40:02.920 --> 40:04.010
the damaged areas at once

40:04.670 --> 40:07.780
to stop the demons from escaping.

40:08.800 --> 40:10.380
As Lilie Valley stretches wide,

40:10.880 --> 40:12.570
repairing seals drains massive spirit power.

40:13.630 --> 40:15.900
Send elite disciples to search

40:16.150 --> 40:17.380
and guard together.

40:17.400 --> 40:17.860
Agreed.

40:18.510 --> 40:19.420
The Sea Calamity draws near,

40:20.280 --> 40:21.460
and the demon clan lurks in wait.

40:21.880 --> 40:22.820
Young disciples

40:23.030 --> 40:25.300
must learn the true threat of demons

40:25.880 --> 40:27.420
and gain battle experience,

40:27.920 --> 40:30.260
or more will be tempted

40:30.510 --> 40:33.260
to practice demonic arts again.

40:35.110 --> 40:35.740
Fair enough.

40:37.110 --> 40:38.420
We'll bring

40:38.960 --> 40:40.340
top disciples

40:40.360 --> 40:41.940
from the tournament

40:42.360 --> 40:43.420
together.

40:45.230 --> 40:45.980
Cuixuan.

40:50.480 --> 40:51.570
Cuixuan,

40:52.320 --> 40:53.900
my disciple hasn't recovered.

40:54.230 --> 40:56.380
Zhuiyu Peak will sit this out.

40:57.590 --> 40:58.130
My apologies.

40:58.710 --> 40:59.260
Sorry.

41:00.230 --> 41:03.570
Our disciples never coddle themselves.

41:04.230 --> 41:05.260
She claimed first place.

41:06.070 --> 41:06.980
Her absence would rouse

41:07.840 --> 41:08.740
doubt among all.

41:11.280 --> 41:12.650
The enemy draws near.

41:13.070 --> 41:14.210
As cultivators,

41:14.550 --> 41:15.900
we must lead the charge

41:16.190 --> 41:17.740
and never flinch.

41:18.630 --> 41:19.420
Elders,

41:19.880 --> 41:22.170
return to your peaks and gather disciples at once.

41:22.320 --> 41:23.570
We depart in two hours.

41:27.030 --> 41:28.460
Understood.

41:28.760 --> 41:29.300
Yes.

41:39.560 --> 41:42.040
[Lilie Valley]

42:09.030 --> 42:11.980
Qin Yangling, Yue Cailing, Deng Xiguang,

42:12.510 --> 42:14.900
Elder Chongyi and I will repair the outer seal.

42:15.070 --> 42:16.260
You will lead disciples

42:16.280 --> 42:17.090
down three separate paths

42:17.360 --> 42:18.130
deep into the valley

42:18.590 --> 42:19.780
to trace the demonic energy.

42:19.800 --> 42:20.300
Me?

42:20.880 --> 42:23.740
Recapture any escaped demons.

42:24.320 --> 42:24.900
Understood.

42:25.550 --> 42:27.530
Most demons here have perished,

42:28.000 --> 42:30.170
yet residual demonic energy lingers for centuries.

42:30.630 --> 42:31.610
It's deadly.

42:32.110 --> 42:33.420
Guard yourselves well

42:33.440 --> 42:34.900
once inside.

42:35.150 --> 42:36.940
Do not let the demonic energy

42:37.320 --> 42:38.170
corrupt your minds.

42:42.050 --> 42:42.300
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.300 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
